

; New file: AstraLing/Utilities/Sound.swift
; A caseless enum Sound mirroring the Haptics pattern — three public static functions (success(), notification(), error()) backed by a private play(_:systemFallback:) that:
; 1. Searches Resources/Sounds/ in the bundle for a named file (success, alert, error) in any of four formats (.caf, .wav, .mp3, .aiff)
; 2. Plays it via AVAudioPlayer (retained in a [String: AVAudioPlayer] dict so it doesn't deallocate mid-playback)
; 3. Falls back to AudioServicesPlaySystemSound with a built-in iOS system sound ID if the file is missing or fails to decode

; New folder: AstraLing/Resources/Sounds/ (with .gitkeep so it's tracked by git and picked up by Xcode's folder-sync). Drop success.caf, alert.caf, and/or error.caf here any time — no code changes needed.

; Sound calls wired to every notification / pop-up dialog:

; ┌───────────────────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────┐
; │                  Surface                  │         Call         │
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ NewPingDialog appears (Merchant)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ PingCancelledDialog appears (Merchant)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ PingRejectedDialog appears (Customer)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ PingSuccessDialog appears (Customer)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ CancelPingDialog appears (Customer)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ Payment success (PaymentView)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ Payment failed alert (PaymentView)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ Payment received (TransaksiBerhasilView)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ Transfer success (TransferBerhasilView)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ Transfer failed alert (TransferSaldoView
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ Profile saved toast (EditProfilView)
; ├───────────────────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────┤
; │ QR saved toast (QRSayaView)
; └───────────────────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────┘                                               
; Mute-switch behavior: respects the silent switch — no AVAudioSession override, so it works in parallel with the QR camera without interference. Haptics still is never fully lost.